Title: Analytical
Definition: Data or function generated using numerical or computational models to simulate the response of a structure under increasing hazard intensities.

Title: Empirical survey
Definition: Data or function generated through regression analysis of historical loss data.

Title: Hybrid
Definition: Data or function generated using data gathered from the international literature.

Title: Judgement
Definition: Data or function generated through the elicitation of expert opinion (heuristic).
